853
01:06:56.137 --> 01:06:58.514
or I'll jump.

854
01:06:58.597 --> 01:07:01.142
-You can scrape up
what's left.
-[Maria] Asia. no.

855
01:07:01.225 --> 01:07:02.518
So selfless.

856
