859
01:07:10.276 --> 01:07:12.319
The fuck
are you talking about?

860
01:07:13.487 --> 01:07:15.781
Didn't you ever think...

861
01:07:15.865 --> 01:07:18.701
How exactly
did your dear sister

862
01:07:18.784 --> 01:07:22.038
