867
01:07:40.848 --> 01:07:42.016
[Maria] Yes.

868
01:07:42.099 --> 01:07:44.060
Splendid.

869
01:07:44.143 --> 01:07:46.604
You will pledge to our Lord.

870
01:07:46.687 --> 01:07:51.567
When the time comes.
you will put your name
on the list.

871
01:07:51.650 --> 01:07:55.321
