[exhales]

974
01:16:16.029 --> 01:16:17.739
This is the only way.

975
01:16:19.700 --> 01:16:21.493
-[blade slashes]
-[grunts]

976
01:16:29.376 --> 01:16:31.378
[somber music playing]

977
