I'm so sorry.

978
01:17:18.675 --> 01:17:19.885
[The Head growls]

979
01:17:19.968 --> 01:17:21.011
Is she dead?

980
01:17:25.265 --> 01:17:26.558
Looks pretty dead to me.

981
01:17:26.642 --> 01:17:27.809
[Asia grunts]

982
01:17:30.312 --> 01:17:32.314
[suspenseful music playing]

983
01:17:44.242 --> 01:17:47.954
